'''塞马耶·克里斯顿'''（{{lang-en|'''Semaj Christon'''}}，{{bd|1992年|11月1日}}），美国职业篮球员，大学曾效力于[[泽维尔大学辛辛那提分校|泽维尔大学辛辛那提分校]]。目前效力于[[中國男子籃球職業聯賽|CBA]][[龍獅籃球俱樂部|廣州龍獅籃球队]]。[http://www.longlions.com/index.php?c=article&id=772] {{Wayback|url=http://www.longlions.com/index.php?c=article&id=772 |date=20171209101556 }}

==大学生涯==
当克里斯顿在{{link-en|布鲁斯特预科学院|Brewster Academy}}毕业后，他选择加入了家乡的泽维尔大学辛辛那提分校。在他的新秀赛季，克里斯顿场均能贡献15.2分和4.6次助攻，得到了[[大西洋赛区|大西洋赛区]]最佳新秀和入选了大西洋赛区第二队<ref>{{cite web | last = Eisenberg | first = Jeff | title = Point guard Semaj Christon aims to lead retooled Xavier back to prominence | work = [[Yahoo!_Sports|Yahoo! Sports]] | date = October 23, 2013 | url = http://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/ncaab-the-dagger/point-guard-semaj-christon-aims-lead-retooled-xavier-202851112--ncaab.html | accessdate = May 14, 2014 | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112031416/http://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/ncaab-the-dagger/point-guard-semaj-christon-aims-lead-retooled-xavier-202851112--ncaab.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在大二赛季，他带领泽维尔大学進入{{link-en|大东区锦标赛|Big East Conference}}，并且以场均17分4.2助攻的数据毫无争议地进入了大东区锦标赛第一队<ref>{{cite web | last = Russell | first = Shannon | title = Semaj Christon unanimous Big East first team pick | work = [[Cincinnati_Enquirer|Cincinnati Enquirer]] | date = March 9, 2014 | url = http://www.cincinnati.com/story/blogs/2014/03/09/semaj-christon-big-east-first-team/6231793/ | accessdate = May 14, 2014 | archive-date = 2019-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191206131420/https://www.cincinnati.com/story/blogs/2014/03/09/semaj-christon-big-east-first-team/6231793/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

==NBA生涯==
2014年3月29日，克里斯顿决定参加[[2014年NBA選秀|NBA选秀]]，放弃他在泽维尔大学的剩余两年学业<ref>{{cite web | last = Giles | first = Matt | title = Xavier’s Semaj Christon bypasses final two years, declares for the 2014 draft | work = [[NBCSports.com|NBCSports.com]] | date = 2014-03-29 | url = http://collegebasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/03/28/xaviers-semaj-christon-forgoes-eligibility-declares-for-the-2014-draft/ | accessdate = May 14, 2014 | archive-date = 2015-04-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150407072250/http://collegebasketballtalk.nbcsports.com/2014/03/28/xaviers-semaj-christon-forgoes-eligibility-declares-for-the-2014-draft/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| title =泽维尔大学二年级控卫克里斯顿将参选| work =[[虎扑体育|虎扑体育]]| date =2014-03-29| url =http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1657614.html| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140913191958/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1657614.html| archivedate =2014-09-13}}</ref>。在选秀大会上，克里斯顿在2轮总第55顺位被[[迈阿密热火|迈阿密热火]]队选中，旋即与[[沙巴兹·内皮尔|沙巴兹·内皮尔]]和{{link-en|P·J·海尔斯顿|P. J. Hairston}}被交易到[[夏洛特黃蜂_(NBA)|夏洛特黄蜂]]<ref>{{cite web| title =PJ-海尔斯顿，浪子回头金不换| work =[[虎扑体育|虎扑体育]]| date =2014-06-28| url =http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1714337.html| access-date =2014-09-13| archive-date =2017-03-08| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170308215926/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1714337.html| dead-url =yes}}</ref>，此后黃蜂隊又爲獲取現金而將他出售至[[俄克拉何马城雷霆|俄克拉何马城雷霆]]<ref>{{cite web| title =黄蜂交易55号秀克里斯顿至雷霆| work =[[虎扑体育|虎扑体育]]| date =2014-06-28| url =http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1713732.html| access-date =2014-09-13| archive-date =2017-03-08| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170308140356/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1713732.html| dead-url =yes}}</ref>。

===俄克拉何马城雷霆时期（[[2014-15_NBA賽季|2014]]-今）===
克里斯顿在{{link-en|2014年NBA夏季联赛|2014 NBA Summer League}}代表雷霆队出战，场均可以拿到11.3分2.8次助攻<ref>{{cite web| title=克里斯顿奥兰多夏季联赛数据| work=NBA.COM| date=2014-07-11| url=http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1714337.html| access-date=2014-09-13| archive-date=2017-03-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308215926/http://voice.hupu.com/nba/1714337.html| dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

